'''埃尔布斯过硫酸盐氧化反应'''（{{lang-de|Elbs-Persulfat-Oxidation}}）指[[酚|酚]]被[[碱性|碱性]][[过二硫酸钾|过二硫酸钾]][[氧化|氧化]]为对位二酚。<ref>Elbs, K. ''J. Prakt. Chem.'' '''1893''', ''48'', 179.</ref>

[[File:Elbs_Persulfate_Oxidation_Scheme.png|center]]

反应产率较低。反应综述：<ref>{{cite journal en| author = S. M. Sethna | title = The Elbs Persulfate Oxidation | year = 1951 | journal = [[Chem._Rev.|Chem. Rev.]] | volume = 49 | issue = 1 | pages = 91–101 | doi = 10.1021/cr60152a002}}</ref><ref>Lee, J. B.; Uff, B. C. ''Quart. Rev.'' '''1967''', ''21'', 453. （综述）</ref><ref>Behrman, E. J. ''Org. React.'' '''1988''', ''35'', 421-511. （综述）</ref>

==反应机理==
酚盐负离子在酚羟基对位对过二硫酸根离子中的过氧原子进行[[亲核|亲核]]进攻，硫酸根离子离去，产生对二酚的[[硫酸酯|硫酸酯]]，经水解得二酚。<ref>{{cite journal en| author = E. J. Behrman | title = The Elbs and Boyland-Sims peroxydisulfate oxidations | year = 2006 | journal = [[Beilstein_Journal_of_Organic_Chemistry|Beilstein Journal of Organic Chemistry]] | volume = 2 | issue = 1 | pages = 22 | doi = 10.1186/1860-5397-2-22}}</ref>

